2. **Modify `src/renderers/SvgCanvas.jsx`** -- Add import and render `<FixtureDefs />` in the plan view tree. Minimal change (2 lines).

3. **Modify `src/renderers/FixtureRenderer.jsx`** -- Replace flat fills with gradient references, update outline stroke, apply shadow filter to fixture groups, rewrite all six `FixtureDetails` switch cases with enhanced internal geometry.

